# Budget Updater Project Overview

This project is a Python-based budget management system that integrates with Google Sheets and uses AI for transaction categorization.

## Main Components

### Core Files
- [main.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/main.py) - The main entry point of the application
- [config.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/config.py) - Configuration management and settings
- [sheets_api.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/sheets_api.py) - Google Sheets integration
- [categorizer.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/categorizer.py) - Transaction categorization logic
- [transformation.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/transformation.py) - Data transformation utilities
- [parsers.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/parsers.py) - Data parsing utilities
- [vertex_ai.py](mdc:Budget_updater/src/budget_updater/vertex_ai.py) - Google Vertex AI integration

### Project Structure
- `src/budget_updater/` - Main package directory
- `tests/` - Test files
- `data/` - Data storage directory
- `credentials/` - API credentials and configuration

